original_client_text.markup_text:
In case you need a glimmer of “Hope,” we got you!
She was born on Sunday, March 19. Since birth, Hope has been receiving around-the-clock care from animal care and veterinary teams. Her mom, eight-year-old Zola, did not show the expected level of maternal care, despite a normal delivery. (Zola is a first-time mom.)
Hope’s condition remains guarded, but she’s getting stronger every day!
#giraffe #omahazoo #zoo #animals #omaha
